    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Warpriest Blessing</strong><br/><br/><p><b>Deities: </b>Gorum, Nethys, Rovagug, Zon-Kuthon.</p><p><b>Destructive Attacks (minor): </b>At 1st level, you can touch an ally and bless it with the power of destruction. For 1 minute, the ally gains a morale bonus on weapon damage rolls equal to half your level (minimum 1).</p><p><b>Heart of Carnage (major): </b>At 10th level, you can touch an ally and bless it with even greater destructive power. For 1 minute, the ally gains a +4 insight bonus on attack rolls made to confirm critical hits and has a 50% chance to treat any critical hit or sneak attack against it as a normal hit.</p>",
